OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775376277
OL,3,CUS and Iran race to find missing crew
OL,4,Cmember after American jet shot down
OL,6,FA second US aircraft, mobilised to
OL,7,Fhelp with the search and rescue
OL,8,Fmission, was also struck in the region
OL,9,Fon Friday.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FPresident Donald Trump declined to
OL,17,Fdiscuss the ongoing search and rescue
OL,18,Fmission on Friday, but told NBC News
OL,19,Fthe incident would not affect
OL,20,Fnegotiations with Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
