OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775376277
OL,3,CUS and Iran race to find missing crew
OL,4,Cmember after American jet shot down
OL,6,F"No, not at all. No, it's war. We're
OL,7,Fin war," Trump said in a brief phone
OL,8,Finterview.
OL,10,FThe president later said "evil and
OL,11,Fwickedness will not prevail" in a
OL,12,Fvideo message shared on Truth Social
OL,13,Ffor Easter.
OL,15,FSo far 13 US service members have died
OL,16,Fin conflict, while 3,527 people have
OL,17,Fdied in Iran according to US-based
OL,18,Frights group Human Rights Activists
OL,19,FNews Agency (HRANA).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
