OL,3,CUS and Iran race to find missing crew
OL,4,Cmember after American jet shot down
OL,6,FLebanese authorities say 1,368 people
OL,7,Fhave been killed and 19 people have
OL,8,Fdied in Israel.
OL,10,FMore than 360 US service members have
OL,11,Fbeen wounded in action in Iran war,
OL,12,Fwith 247 of them being Army soldiers.
OL,14,FTwo US aircrafts downed over Iran
OL,16,FThe US F15-E Strike Eagle fighter jet
OL,17,Fwas shot down by Iran on Friday, with
OL,18,Fone service member - reported to be
OL,19,Fthe pilot - already rescued, according
OL,20,Fto US officials.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
