PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775376277
OL,3,CUS and Iran race to find missing crew
OL,4,Cmember after American jet shot down
OL,6,FThe second crew member, a weapons
OL,7,Fsystems officer, remains missing with
OL,8,Fa large-scale search and rescue
OL,9,Foperation in place.
OL,11,FA US A-10 aircraft mobilised to help
OL,12,Ffind the downed crew member was also
OL,13,Fstruck by Iran on Friday, forcing the
OL,14,Fpilot to eject, an official familiar
OL,15,Fwith the incident told CNN. They have
OL,16,Fsince been rescued.
OL,18,FIranian state media claimed the
OL,19,Faircraft was hit by Iranian air
OL,20,Fdefenses, citing Iran's Army public
OL,21,Frelations office.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775376277
OL,3,CUS and Iran race to find missing crew
OL,4,Cmember after American jet shot down
OL,6,FThe pilot of the A-10, a single-seat
OL,7,Faircraft also known by the nickname
OL,8,FWarthog, able to fly out of Iranian
OL,9,Fterritory before ejecting, the
OL,10,Fofficial said.
OL,12,FIsrael is assisting the US search
OL,13,Foperation with intelligence, but is
OL,14,Fnot active in any on-the-ground rescue.
OL,16,FThe last time a US fighter jet was
OL,17,Fshot down by enemy fire in combat was
OL,18,Fduring the 2003 invasion of Iraq -
OL,19,Fmore than two decades ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
