OL,3,CUS and Iran race to find missing crew
OL,4,Cmember after American jet shot down
OL,6,FA reward equivalent to $60,000 (about
OL,7,F#45,000) is on offer to those who are
OL,8,Fsuccessful, some state news
OL,9,Forganisations have said.
OL,11,FThe speaker of Iran's parliament took
OL,12,Fto X to mock the US on Friday,
OL,13,Fsarcastically praising the nation's
OL,14,F"incredible progress" in the war.
OL,16,F"After defeating Iran 37 times in a
OL,17,Frow, this brilliant no-strategy war
OL,18,Fthey started has now been downgraded
OL,19,Ffrom 'regime change' to 'Hey! Can
OL,20,Fanyone find our pilots? Please?'"
OL,21,FMohammad Bagher Ghalibaf said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
